quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,62,"'in hdha aldhy anbatk bih min 'amr eisaa lahu alnaba alhaqu aldhy la shaka fyh, wama min mebwd yastahiqu alebadt 'iilaa allah whdh, wa'iina allah lahu aleaziz fi mlkh, alhakim fi tdbyrh wfelh"
  3,63,"f'in 'aeraduu ean tsdyqk watbaek fahum almfsdwn, wallah ealim bhm, wsyjazyhm ealaa dhlk"
  3,64,"ql -ayha alrswl- li'ahl alkitab min alyhwd walnsara: tealawa 'iilaa kalimat eadl wahaqa naltazim biha jmyeana: wahi 'ana nakhus allah wahdah balebadt, wala natakhidh 'aya sharik meh, min wthn 'aw snm 'aw slyb 'aw taghwt 'aw ghyr dhlk, wala yudin baeduna libaed baltaet min dun allh. fa'iin 'aeraduu ean hadhih aldaewat altayibat faquluu lahum - 'ayuha almuminun -: ashhaduu ealayna bi'anaa muslimun mnqadwn lrbna balebwdyt wal'ikhlas. waldaewat 'iilaa kalimat swa', kama tujjah 'iilaa alyhwd walnsara, twjjah 'iilaa min jaraa mjrahm"
  3,65,"ya 'ashab alkutub almnzlt min alyhwd walnsara, kayf yujadil kl minkum fi 'an 'iibrahim ealayh alslam kan ealaa mllath, wama 'unzlt altawrat wal'iinjil 'iilaa min bedh? 'afala tafqahun khataan qwlkm: 'iina 'iibrahim kan yhwdyaan 'aw nsranyaan, waqad ealimtum 'ana alyahudiat walnsranyt hadathat baed wafatih bhyn?"
  3,66,"ha 'antum ya hwla' jadaltum rasul allah mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam fima lakum bih eilm min 'amr dynkm, mimaa tetqdwn sihatih fi ktbkm, flim tjadlwn fima lays lakum bih eilm min 'amr 'ibrahym? wallah yaelam al'umur ealaa khfayha, wa'antum la telmwn"
  3,67,"ma kan 'iibrahim yhwdyaan wala nsranyaan, falam takun alyahudiat wala alnsranyt 'iilaa man bedh, wlkn kan mtbeana li'amr allah wtaeth, mstslmana lrbh, wama kan min almshrkyn"
  3,68,"'inn 'ahaqu alnaas bi'iibrahim wakhshm bh, aladhin amanuu bih wsdqu brsalth watabieuh ealaa dynh, whdha alnabii muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam waladhin amanuu bh. wallah wly almuminin bih almtbeyn shreh"
  3,69,"tmnnat jamaeat min alyhwd walnsara law yudiluwnakum - 'ayuha almuslimun - ean al'islam, wama yudiluwn 'iilaa 'anfusahum watbaehm, wama ydrwn dhlk wala yelmwnh"
  3,70,"ya 'ahl altawrat wal'iinjil lm tjhdwn ayat allah alati anzlha ealaa rusulah fi ktbkm, wafiha 'ana mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam hu alrasul almntzr, wa'ana ma ja'akum bih hu alhq, wa'antum tashhadun bdhlk? wlknkm tnkrwnh"